---++ *OSG Council Face-to-Face Meeting*

---++ Logistics
   * *OSG Council Dinner*
      * Date: Tuesday  August 17th, 2010
      * Time: Drinks at 6:30PM, Dinner at 7:00PM 
      * Location: Fermilab Chez Leon
      * Directions: [[http://www.fnal.gov/directorate/OPMO/mapsdirections/WilsonHalltoChezLeon.pdf][See Map]]

   * *OSG Council Face-to-Face Meeting*
      * Date: Wednesday August 18th, 2010 
      * Time: 9:00AM Central - 5:00PM Central
      * Location: Fermilab: Wilson Hall, Hornet’s Nest 8th floor crossover
      * Teleconferencing: 866-740-1260 ... Access Code: 8403921

---++ Attending

   * Kent Blackburn (co-chair), Paul Avery (co-chair), Scott McCauley (Indiana), Chander Sehgal (Fermilab), , Rob Quick (Indiana), Horst Severini (OU/DOSAR), Mine Altunay (Fermilab), Rob Gardner (UChicago), Shaowen Wang (NCSA/UIUC), Victoria White (Fermilab), Frank Wuerthwein (UCSD), Dan Fraser (Argonne), Tom Hacker (Purdue), Piotr Sliz (HMS), Ruth Pordes (Fermilab), Michael Ernst (BNL), Steve Tuecke (Globus/UChicago/ANL), David Swanson (HCC), Brian Bockelman (HCC), Miron Livny (UofWisc-Madison), Qishong Li (Fermilab/CD/DO), Brad Abbot (D0/Oklahoma)
   * Remote Participants: Doug Olson (LBNL), Ron Soltz (ALICE-USA)

---++ Agenda Wednesday  August 18th, 2010

---+++ Overview:
   * The focus for this OSG Council Face-To-Face Meeting will be planning, scope, and organization for the renewal of OSG Funding (OSG')
   * Mission Statement
   * iSGTW Update
   * Plans from the Major Stakeholders
   * Adding new Major Stakeholders | NIH role as a funding agency
   * OSG' | ExTenCI | XD interface
   * Report from August 17th Focus Meeting
   * Looking for good discussion and progress


---+++ Morning Session 9:00AM to Noon Central

   * 9:00AM - 9:15AM Welcome / Sign-In / Announcements (Kent/Paul)
